data.description: Charming home in downtown Kalispell. 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom on the main floor. Living room and kitchen are very spacious. Great for entertaining guests. Very central location for easy access to restaurants , grocery stores, and other downtown events. Main floor is 1072 sq ft and the unfinished basement adds another 869 sq ft of space for a total  of 1941 sq ft. This unfinished basement could be made into a home business and add a home gym or hobby room.  Zoned for many potential business possibilities. No HOA. 1 stall garage. Call Denise Morken @ 406-885-6551 or your Real Estate Professional
